Package nz.ac.vuw.ecs.swen225.gp22.domain

Class Chap

java.lang.Object
nz.ac.vuw.ecs.swen225.gp22.domain.Chap
All Implemented Interfaces:
Entity
public class Chap extends Object implements Entity
Author:
Leo Gaynor: 300437633

The Chap class represents the internal state of Chap. The class provides methods for utility and moving the Chap object through the maze. It has extensive built in movement and interaction safety, preventing IllegalStateExceptions and IllegalArgumentExceptions.
